{
  "stem": "9156.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They always talk about one village, which was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I tell you, there were many villages that were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in that village, the mayor had decided that he lets refugees come in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He will give them false-- they can get false papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they can be, somehow, kept there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, when we got to Lavit, there was that mayor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave us a paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what did you want to be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were Belgians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because when you are Belgian-- I spoke perfect French, so that's all right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They speak that in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Paul spoke very good Plattdeutsch, you know, the northern part of Germany?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He could speak that-- which is what they speak in the Flemish part.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were a very good Belgian couple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I can't tell you the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they gave us-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what would I call it?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a stable, literally, a stable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to crawl in, like an animal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Who gave this to you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mayor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever he had, they gave us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was what they had, a stable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you crawled in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My legs were not like they are  now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you crawled in there, and you slept on the straw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm doing this fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- and that was literally hidden in Lavit, because the German police-- or not police.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had no right to do that, but they came all the time, looking where there were people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did this stable belong to a family?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were Belgian refugees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took care of Belgian refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very nice to Belgian refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
